" indenting
" nnoremap <tab> >>
" nnoremap <s-tab> <<
" vnoremap <tab> >
" vnoremap <s-tab> <
" inoremap <tab> <c-t>
" inoremap <s-tab> <c-d>

" split line (compliment of <s-j> to join)
nnoremap <s-k> h<cr>^

" Helpful for with goto definition or reference doesnt work
" pair with fzf or find_* bash commands
nnoremap <silent> <leader>yw "+yiw

" navigation
